{"tid":635821,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"逾六千市民捐款　34人捐689元","createTime":"2018-04-20T10:58:05.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-20T12:46:03.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"60b070dfa37f3d274f5f67b862155463e12addf8","tid":635821,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-20T10:58:05.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180420/20367013?_ga=2.103981696.1029761066.1520127978-1555213041.1517019171\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180420%2F20367013%3F_ga%3D2.103981696.1029761066.1520127978-1555213041.1517019171&d=F7LzYusczQOdPG6krgBM08PrXSGIZiPsBFv3mRhlVuk%3D&h=acce5812\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180420%2F20367013%3F_ga%3D2.103981696.1029761066.1520127978-1555213041.1517019171&h=06b546fc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180420/20367013?_ga=2.103981696.1029761066.1520127978-1555213041.1517019171</a><br />\n<br />\n逾六千市民捐款　34人捐689元<br />\n<br />\n3.6K<br />\n港聞<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180420/large/0419irene5203.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180420%2Flarge%2F0419irene5203.jpg&h=53de9e33&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n天下為公<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】「天下為公」眾籌發起10天至昨日為止，已籌得逾217萬元，捐款人數達6,147人。尹兆堅指大部份是小額捐款，最多為100至500元的捐款，而比較特別的捐款，是有34位巿民捐款689元，亦有30多位人士捐出一些「零頭數」，目的是嘗試將捐款尾數拼湊成「689」，「咁我相信呢啲行為，都反映佢哋嘅心態，認同要追究梁振英今次UGL事件」。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n最大額捐兩萬<br />\n<br />\n尹兆堅指，今次最大額的捐款是有一人捐兩萬元，另有10多人捐一萬元，指計劃「究竟係一粒子彈，定係一粒炮彈？就視乎我哋有幾多糧草」。他又指建制派之中，除了早前公開捐款一千元的自由黨榮譽主席田北俊外，有小部份建制派議員在計劃公佈後，在立法會向他「豎起手指公」，令他覺得不少建制派議員私下都認為有需要查出真相。<br />\n<br />\n■記者林俊謙<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞<br />\n<br />\n梁稱與UGL協商離職獲DTZ同意天下為公促梁振英14日內交證據<br />\n<br />\n港聞 5小時前"},{"pid":"fcbe7bd1378e1a113534fce6782230143b51e554","tid":635821,"uid":83097,"like":15,"dislike":1,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-20T10:59:54.000Z","msg":"嘩政府好撚驚呀 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n嘩我地又可以引起國際關注上外國新聞好威威呀 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c4066e91d780418431a1126ee16b3b2c90a21ab6","tid":635821,"uid":157362,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-20T11:02:35.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f9ba2653fd3a06bf0f01b2cda3e990daa84d6dba","tid":635821,"uid":34103,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-20T11:02:54.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a35413ef04332cc0accd82e460793a1dbb5e915c","tid":635821,"uid":61280,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-20T11:09:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>老實講<br />\n梁振英唔同曾蔭權<br />\n<br />\n曾蔭權背後無中共撐<br />\n梁振英直情係佢隻狗<br />\n<br />\n你預呢單野燒錢都得啦</blockquote><br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">你估呢班戲子唔心水清咩？？呢單野應該先正名&quot;天下為供&quot;囉屌！！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n根本有心撚狗但又唔會得罪佢地同689共同既主人，旨在屌住黎走，燒時間厄飯食兼長賣下廣告！！！</span></strong></span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e82e87b78e98f343f4c58918a3023ccff75a214d","tid":635821,"uid":50457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-20T11:14:08.000Z","msg":"689 ！777！<br />\n689！777！"},{"pid":"02cb69408ef77926c1377b8e315e1f95d5a64ab8","tid":635821,"uid":157362,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-20T11:16:00.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d9a2613f66ff4ea85acf7f0528c7e7cfb8bd1fd1","tid":635821,"uid":53254,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e82e87b78e98f343f4c58918a3023ccff75a214d","tid":635821,"uid":50457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTim